{"type":"message","id":"3115ad9f","parentId":"9ed1017a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:15:19.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要先检查今天是否已收盘，然后清空 realtime-data.txt 文件，为获取实时数据做准备。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我需要先检查今天是否收盘，然后获取实时数据。让我先检查交易日状态并清空实时数据文件。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_284a6a2e84174cac88649e65","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 -c \"\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 获取交易日历，检查今天是否交易日\nimport datetime\ntoday = datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ncal = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\nif cal.empty:\n    print('MARKET_CLOSED')\nelse:\n    print('MARKET_OPEN')\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa13922c39aa415ba1d68de9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"> ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773119711176}}
